Title: Multi Arena
Description:
This is a scpecial arena-type endless level, which changes depending on the enemy group.
In other words, each level arena will look slightly different (see screenshots).

Includes:
6 Bronze levels
3 Silver levels
3 Gold levels
3 Diamod levels
9 Titanium levels

Stepping on pressure plates (big red squares) opens rooms or lowers platforms. Not every layout has pressure plates!

There're 17 layouts in total, so some levels have repeating layouts.

Keywords: Castle, Dynamic, Corridors, Lava, Traps, Buttons
